### Test TurboVets API

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api

### 2. Login (you need to create a user first - see seed-data.ts)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "owner@turbovets.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Create Task (replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN with the token from login response)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "title": "Complete patient checkup",
  "description": "Annual checkup for Max the dog",
  "category": "Veterinary"
}

### 4. Get All Tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### 5. Get Single Task
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### 6. Update Task
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "status": "InProgress",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### 7. Delete Task (only Owner/Admin can do this)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
